Dialogue: 1,0:01:52.68,0:01:55.68,Title,,0,0,0,,{\blur1\pos(675,510)}from Felicity Awhile
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.68,0:01:55.68,underTitle,,0,0,0,,{\blur8\pos(675,510)}from Felicity Awhile
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.19,0:01:59.84,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（不破真広）絶園の魔法使い？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.40,0:01:59.60,Default,,0,0,0,,The mage of Exodus?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.60,0:02:01.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Is there really such a person?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.84,0:02:02.41,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,そんなの\N本当にいるのかよ!?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.41,0:02:04.98,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（葉風）私の誕生は\Nはじまりの樹の覚醒が→
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.43,0:02:06.57,Default,,0,0,0,,My birth means that the revival of the Tree of Genesis is getting closer.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.98,0:02:07.00,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,近づいた証しであり→
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.98,0:02:11.82,Default,,0,0,0,,My role is to decide when it will fully revive.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.00,0:02:09.62,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,私は　その完全覚醒のときを→
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.62,0:02:12.40,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,決める役割を担わされている。→
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.40,0:02:14.91,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（通信）私が\Nしかるべき時機と意志のもと→
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.59,0:02:14.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Unless I decide that it is time
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.91,0:02:19.41,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,一定の手続きを踏まんかぎり\Nはじまりの樹の完全覚醒はならん。
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.97,0:02:16.85,Default,,0,0,0,,and perform the necessary procedures,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.85,0:02:19.04,Default,,0,0,0,,the Tree of Genesis cannot be completely resurrected.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.41,0:02:22.23,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（葉風）\Nだからこそ　左門は　私を封じ→
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.62,0:02:22.26,Default,,0,0,0,,That's why Samon sealed me away,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.23,0:02:24.98,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,完全覚醒を遅らせようとしたのだ。
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.26,0:02:24.59,Default,,0,0,0,,to try and delay the revival.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.98,0:02:28.87,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（滝川吉野）けど　そんな\N大きな役割を　なぜ葉風さんに？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.05,0:02:28.55,Default,,0,0,0,,But why were {\i1}you{\i0} given such a huge task, Ms. Hakaze?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.87,0:02:32.66,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（葉風）神とても\N覚醒という大きな変動を→
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.06,0:02:30.43,Default,,0,0,0,,It may be a god,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.43,0:02:35.47,Default,,0,0,0,,but it does not allow a change as drastic as its resurrection to be decided by its own whim.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.66,0:02:36.24,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,己の勝手なときに起こすのは\Nよしとせん。
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.24,0:02:38.68,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,私は　人の代表として→
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.48,0:02:38.64,Default,,0,0,0,,I have been chosen to represent humanity,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.64,0:02:41.73,Default,,0,0,0,,to decide when the time for revival is right.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.68,0:02:41.98,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,そのときを\N判断する役割を与えられたのだ。
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.40,0:02:47.90,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,そんな　はじまりの樹が\N現在の文明を食い尽くし→
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.52,0:02:47.99,Default,,0,0,0,,There is no way that the Tree of Genesis is such a cruel deity
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.90,0:02:52.44,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,現存生物を死滅させるといった\N無慈悲な存在であるはずがない！
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.99,0:02:52.07,Default,,0,0,0,,that it would devour all of civilization and doom all living creatures!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.44,0:02:56.46,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（左門）しかし　姫様\Nあなたは　はじまりの樹を盲信し→
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.61,0:02:54.30,Default,,0,0,0,,However, Princess...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.30,0:02:56.66,Default,,0,0,0,,You have blind faith in the Tree of Genesis
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.46,0:02:59.28,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,危険性など\N僅かも顧みられない！→
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.66,0:02:59.04,Default,,0,0,0,,and will not see its potential threat.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.28,0:03:01.67,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（通信）そんな　あなたに\N正しい意志と時機が→
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.47,0:03:03.92,Default,,0,0,0,,How can you truly determine the appropriate time for the Tree's revival?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.67,0:03:03.92,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,お分かりになると言えますか？→
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.92,0:03:08.50,Default,,0,0,0,,The Tree of Genesis putting its fate in the hands of mere mortals is an illusion.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.92,0:03:06.69,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,はじまりの樹が\N人の意志に委ねているなど→
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.69,0:03:09.18,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,まやかしにすぎません！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.18,0:03:13.35,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,絶園の樹を見張らせる鎖部一族を\N従わせやすくするため→
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.26,0:03:13.45,Default,,0,0,0,,It only made us believe we had such privilege to guarantee our dedication
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.35,0:03:16.35,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,そのような特権があると\N思わせただけです！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.45,0:03:15.97,Default,,0,0,0,,to the task of keeping watch over the Tree of Exodus!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.18,0:03:18.06,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't care about any of that!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.35,0:03:18.60,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,そういうのは　どうでもいい！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.58,0:03:20.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Is there or is there not
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.60,0:03:22.00,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,絶園の魔法使いは\Nいるのか!?　いねぇのか!?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.56,0:03:21.97,Default,,0,0,0,,a mage of Exodus?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.33,0:03:32.92,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,絶園の樹が\N己の復活を感じたとき→
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.39,0:03:32.42,Default,,0,0,0,,As the Tree of Exodus felt its revival approach,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.78,0:03:37.66,Default,,0,0,0,,I cannot say it is impossible that a mage of Exodus could have been created,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.92,0:03:35.37,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,はじまりの樹の覚醒に合わせて→
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.37,0:03:38.15,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,姫様が　お生まれになったように→
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.15,0:03:42.14,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,絶園の魔法使いが\N生まれた可能性はないでもない。→
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.23,0:03:41.49,Default,,0,0,0,,in the same way the princess was born.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.04,0:03:43.43,Default,,0,0,0,,However,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.14,0:03:44.81,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,しかし　その絶園の魔法使いが→
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.43,0:03:46.98,Default,,0,0,0,,neither can it be said that this mage of Exodus is the one
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.81,0:03:49.12,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,お前の妹を殺した犯人とは\Nまだ言えん！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.98,0:03:48.00,Default,,0,0,0,,that killed your sister!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.12,0:03:53.24,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,けどよ\N絶園の魔法使いが犯人なら→
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.43,0:03:53.30,Default,,0,0,0,,But if the mage of Exodus is the murderer,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.24,0:03:57.67,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,そいつが　はじまりの樹に操られて\N愛花を殺したって仮説は→
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.30,0:03:57.26,Default,,0,0,0,,the theory that the Tree of Genesis controlled that person to kill my sister
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.26,0:03:59.43,Default,,0,0,0,,no longer stands, does it?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.67,0:03:59.77,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,成り立たないんじゃねぇか？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.87,0:04:03.42,Default,,0,0,0,,In this world,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.93,0:04:04.45,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,絶園の樹は　この世で唯一→
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.42,0:04:07.45,Default,,0,0,0,,only the Tree of Exodus has the power to exceed the Tree of Genesis.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.45,0:04:07.97,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,はじまりの樹の理を\N超える力を持つ。
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.97,0:04:10.00,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,なら　その分身である者が→
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.01,0:04:10.03,Default,,0,0,0,,So it's hard to imagine
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.00,0:04:13.81,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,はじまりの樹に操られるなんて\N考えにくい。
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.03,0:04:13.07,Default,,0,0,0,,that the Tree of Genesis could control the other one's avatar.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.81,0:04:18.08,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,現に　はじまりの樹の魔法探査にも\N引っ掛かってないんだ。
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.90,0:04:17.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Moreover, the avatar wouldn't be snared by the \NTree of Genesis's magical investigation either.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.08,0:04:20.11,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,だとしたら→
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.24,0:04:19.92,Default,,0,0,0,,If that's the case,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.92,0:04:23.37,Default,,0,0,0,,it means that the mage of Exodus just happened to kill Aika.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.11,0:04:23.42,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,絶園の魔法使いが\Nたまたま　愛花を殺し→
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.37,0:04:26.45,Default,,0,0,0,,The Tree of Genesis then saw an opportunity
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.42,0:04:26.40,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,それを利用できると考えた\Nはじまりの樹が→
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.40,0:04:31.57,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,俺と葉風を結び付けた…\Nって考えた方が自然になるな。
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.45,0:04:28.64,Default,,0,0,0,,and put me in touch with Hakaze.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.64,0:04:31.21,Default,,0,0,0,,That would be the reasonable conclusion to draw.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.57,0:04:36.11,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,それなら　愛花ちゃんの死に\Nはじまりの樹は関係ない。
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.75,0:04:32.94,Default,,0,0,0,,If we use that theory,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.94,0:04:35.71,Default,,0,0,0,,then the Tree of Genesis would have nothing to do with Aika's death.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.25,0:04:42.59,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,逆に　絶園の樹の方に\N大きく責任があるってことになる。
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.48,0:04:42.47,Default,,0,0,0,,In fact, it would imply that the Tree of Exodus was largely responsible.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.47,0:04:48.40,Default,,0,0,0,,And if a mage of Exodus has been born in response to the Tree of Exodus's revival,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.59,0:04:45.64,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,そして　絶園の樹の復活を感じて→
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.64,0:04:48.64,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,絶園の魔法使いが\N生まれたのなら…。
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.67,0:04:54.74,Default,,0,0,0,,then you, Kusaribe Samon, who has sped up the Tree's revival,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.74,0:04:55.11,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,その復活を\N積極的に進めた鎖部左門→
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.11,0:04:59.01,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,お前も　間接的に\N愛花の死に手を貸したことになる。
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.20,0:04:58.83,Default,,0,0,0,,can be considered to have had a hand in Aika's death, as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.92,0:05:03.94,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（心の声）≪そうだ≫
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.24,0:05:03.29,Defalics,,0,0,0,,He's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.83,0:05:05.87,Defalics,,0,0,0,,Everything's been turned on its head.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.94,0:05:06.41,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,≪すべてが　ひっくり返る≫
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.33,0:05:09.58,Defalics,,0,0,0,,Samon's logic for fighting the Tree of Genesis
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.41,0:05:10.06,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,≪左門の　はじまりの樹を\N倒すべきという理屈は→
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.02,0:05:14.59,Defalics,,0,0,0,,has been applied to Mahiro \Nfighting the Tree of Exodus instead.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.06,0:05:14.16,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,そのまま　真広が　絶園の樹を\N倒すという理屈に反転される≫
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.53,0:05:17.42,Defalics,,0,0,0,,Kusaribe Samon has lost.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.59,0:05:17.69,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,≪鎖部左門の負けだ≫
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.51,0:05:21.76,Default,,0,0,0,,It appears that this is over, Samon.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.51,0:05:22.36,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（葉風・通信）\N詰んだようだな　左門。→
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.36,0:05:25.11,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,あとは　私が供物を見つけ→
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.42,0:05:24.56,Default,,0,0,0,,All that remains is for me to find the offering,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.06,0:05:26.54,Default,,0,0,0,,and return to your time.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.11,0:05:27.73,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,そちらに戻るのみ。
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.07,0:05:34.37,Defalics,,0,0,0,,Can this really be allowed to happen?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.17,0:05:35.27,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（左門）\N≪こんなことがあっていいのか？≫
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.27,0:05:38.34,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,≪逆転を期して放った\N自らの理論に→
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.43,0:05:37.86,Defalics,,0,0,0,,The theory I'd revealed in order to mount a comeback
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.34,0:05:42.01,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ものの見事に\N返り討たれるとは…≫
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.41,0:05:41.04,Defalics,,0,0,0,,has instead been turned completely against me!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.01,0:05:45.80,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,≪これが\Nはじまりの樹に支配された→
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.14,0:05:45.84,Defalics,,0,0,0,,Is this the logic of the world
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.80,0:05:48.30,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,世界の理なのか!?≫
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.84,0:05:48.66,Defalics,,0,0,0,,ruled by the Tree of Genesis?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.94,0:05:55.32,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（早河）どういうことだ？\N（部下）新たに発生した樹は→
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.10,0:05:53.38,Defalics,,0,0,0,,What's going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.78,0:05:58.66,Defalics,,0,0,0,,It's been reported that the newly observed tree \Nappears to be absorbing metallicized life forms.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.32,0:05:59.33,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,金属化した生物を\N吸収しているように見えると…。
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.33,0:06:02.42,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（早河）≪今までのデータにないぞ\Nこんな現象≫
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.34,0:06:02.40,Defalics,,0,0,0,,This didn't happen before.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.40,0:06:03.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Reporting!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.42,0:06:05.13,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（局員）報告！\N（早河）なんだ？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.80,0:06:05.05,Default,,0,0,0,,What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.05,0:06:10.40,Default,,0,0,0,,The plant-like object is turning all humans \Nand man-made objects along its path into ash.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.13,0:06:08.40,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（局員）植物状の物体は\N接触した建造物や人工物を→
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.40,0:06:11.24,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,すべて塵にしています！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.24,0:06:14.88,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,文明を食らっているのか？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.50,0:06:14.38,Default,,0,0,0,,It's devouring civilization?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.99,0:06:34.76,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（山本）\Nはじまりの樹って…　あれが？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.22,0:06:32.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Is that really
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.36,0:06:34.73,Default,,0,0,0,,the Tree of Genesis?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.73,0:06:38.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, though that is merely a shadow of its true self.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.76,0:06:38.80,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（潤一郎）ええ。　ただし\Nごくごく一部にすぎないでしょう。
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.63,0:06:40.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Mr. Junichiro,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.80,0:06:40.84,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（夏村）潤一郎殿→
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.84,0:06:44.14,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,本当に　はじまりの樹が\N覚醒したのですか？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.85,0:06:44.05,Default,,0,0,0,,has the Tree of Genesis truly revived?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.05,0:06:48.22,Default,,0,0,0,,As far as I know, Hakaze hasn't approved it.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.14,0:06:48.76,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（潤一郎）葉風ちゃんは　その決定を\N行っていないはずだけど…。
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.76,0:06:52.96,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,≪それとも　これもまた\N何か必然の出来事なのか？≫
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.80,0:06:53.10,Defalics,,0,0,0,,Or is this yet another inevitable event?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.43,0:06:57.27,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,≪左門の負けは確定した≫
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.49,0:06:57.07,Defalics,,0,0,0,,Samon's defeat has been decided.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.27,0:07:00.24,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,≪こうなれば\N孤島にある供物の隠し場所を→
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.46,0:07:01.71,Defalics,,0,0,0,,At this point, we should make him tell us where the offering is on the island.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.24,0:07:03.64,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,しゃべらせるべきだ。　なのに→
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.51,0:07:03.57,Defalics,,0,0,0,,So then,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.57,0:07:06.15,Defalics,,0,0,0,,why aren't you making a move, Mahiro?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.64,0:07:07.18,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,なぜ動かないんだ　真広≫
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.95,0:07:08.69,Defalics,,0,0,0,,I don't like it.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.18,0:07:09.25,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,≪気に入らねぇ≫
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.23,0:07:11.98,Defalics,,0,0,0,,Things are working out too well for Hakaze.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.25,0:07:12.84,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,≪葉風にとって\Nうまくいきすぎてやがる≫
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.71,0:07:15.54,Defalics,,0,0,0,,What kind of miracle is this,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.84,0:07:15.59,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,≪こんなきれいに\N逆転が決まるなんて→
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.54,0:07:17.34,Defalics,,0,0,0,,that the reversal goes so well?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.59,0:07:17.74,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,どんな奇跡だよ≫
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.69,0:07:19.41,Defalics,,0,0,0,,Even if I were to help Samon,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.74,0:07:22.29,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,≪左門に手を貸しても\N愛花を殺した犯人は見つからねぇ≫
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.41,0:07:22.33,Defalics,,0,0,0,,I wouldn't be able to find Aika's killer.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.29,0:07:24.65,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,≪それどころか　左門の野郎が→
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.33,0:07:23.55,Defalics,,0,0,0,,Not only that,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.55,0:07:27.27,Defalics,,0,0,0,,but Samon may be part of the reason she died.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.65,0:07:28.30,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,愛花の殺された\N原因かもしれねぇくらいだ≫
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.30,0:07:30.34,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,≪だが→
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.77,0:07:33.81,Defalics,,0,0,0,,But if this is all something that the Tree of Genesis willed to happen,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.34,0:07:33.87,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,もし　これが　はじまりの樹の\N仕組んだことなら→
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.81,0:07:38.07,Defalics,,0,0,0,,perhaps it made it seem like there was a mage of Exodus,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.87,0:07:38.38,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,あたかも　絶園の魔法使いが\N実在するかのように見せかけ→
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.07,0:07:42.54,Defalics,,0,0,0,,to force me to side with Hakaze.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.38,0:07:42.58,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,俺が葉風に肩入れする状況を\N作ったって可能性もある≫
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.00,0:07:46.32,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,≪確かに　そうだ≫
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.02,0:07:45.42,Defalics,,0,0,0,,It's certainly true.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.32,0:07:50.97,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,≪偽らないまでも　魔法探査に\N引っ掛からないようにするだけで→
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.33,0:07:50.98,Defalics,,0,0,0,,The Tree may have simply made it look as though a mage of Exodus exists
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.97,0:07:55.95,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,絶園の魔法使いがいるかのように\N錯覚させることは可能≫
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.98,0:07:55.07,Defalics,,0,0,0,,by shielding the perpetrator from the web of magic...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.71,0:07:58.29,Defalics,,0,0,0,,But if the Tree of Genesis is behind this,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.95,0:07:58.45,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,≪はじまりの樹が犯人なら→
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.29,0:08:01.05,Defalics,,0,0,0,,shouldn't Hakaze be the one I shoot?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.45,0:08:02.07,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,俺の討つべき相手は\N葉風じゃねぇのか？≫
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.07,0:08:07.01,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,≪けど　今も葉風さんは\N必死に供物を探している≫
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.13,0:08:06.18,Defalics,,0,0,0,,But even now, Ms. Hakaze is desperately looking for the offering.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.01,0:08:09.91,Defalics,,0,0,0,,If Ms. Hakaze is the true culprit,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.01,0:08:09.89,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,≪もし本当に\Nはじまりの樹が犯人なら→
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.89,0:08:13.05,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,もっと簡単に\N供物が見つかってるはずだ≫
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.91,0:08:12.77,Defalics,,0,0,0,,she should have been able to find it far more easily.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.77,0:08:14.78,Defalics,,0,0,0,,Will I really be able
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.05,0:08:15.36,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,≪葉風に手を貸して　本当に→
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.78,0:08:17.54,Defalics,,0,0,0,,to track down the killer by siding with Hakaze?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.36,0:08:17.80,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,犯人にたどりつけるのか？≫
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.54,0:08:21.38,Defalics,,0,0,0,,The killer could be the Tree of Genesis.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.80,0:08:21.87,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,≪犯人は　はじまりの樹かも\Nしれねぇんだぞ≫
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.87,0:08:25.84,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,≪真広　今は　はじまりの樹を…→
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.95,0:08:25.37,Defalics,,0,0,0,,Mahiro, right now, we should believe in the Tree of Gen—
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.84,0:08:29.16,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,いや　葉風さんを信じるべきだ≫
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.87,0:08:28.98,Defalics,,0,0,0,,No, we should believe in Ms. Hakaze.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.42,0:08:36.75,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,≪もはや　私に打つ手はない≫
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.47,0:08:35.48,Defalics,,0,0,0,,There is nothing I can do.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.75,0:08:38.79,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,≪だが→
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.31,0:08:38.13,Defalics,,0,0,0,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.79,0:08:41.81,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,あの少年が\N魔具を持ったまま動かんのなら→
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.86,0:08:41.89,Defalics,,0,0,0,,As long as that boy holds the talisman without firing it,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.81,0:08:44.06,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,まだ望みはある≫
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.89,0:08:43.51,Defalics,,0,0,0,,there is still hope.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.05,0:08:47.65,Defalics,,0,0,0,,If the Tree of Exodus can be revived before the princess returns,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.06,0:08:47.73,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,≪姫様が戻る前に\N絶園の樹復活が間に合えば→
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.65,0:08:49.51,Defalics,,0,0,0,,we may yet manage to win.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.73,0:08:50.62,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,勝てないことはない≫
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.62,0:08:54.20,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（葉風）\N≪左門　供物をどこに隠した!?≫
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.83,0:08:54.25,Defalics,,0,0,0,,Samon, where did you hide the offering?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.26,0:09:01.31,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（左門）≪姫様→
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.45,0:09:00.31,Defalics,,0,0,0,,Princess,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.29,0:09:04.71,Defalics,,0,0,0,,with only the information you have, it will take you at least two—
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.31,0:09:04.73,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,今ある情報だけで\N供物を見つけるのには　２時間…→
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.71,0:09:08.45,Defalics,,0,0,0,,no, perhaps one hour to find it.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.73,0:09:08.33,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,いや\N１時間は　最低かかるはずです≫
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.54,0:09:12.91,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,≪こればかりは　自分で見つける≫
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.57,0:09:12.54,Defalics,,0,0,0,,I shall find it on my own.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.91,0:09:15.57,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,≪はじまりの樹に祈りはせん！≫
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.98,0:09:15.08,Defalics,,0,0,0,,I will not pray to the Tree of Genesis!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.57,0:09:19.50,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（左門）\N≪その間　何事もなく過ぎれば→
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.59,0:09:18.55,Defalics,,0,0,0,,Provided nothing else interferes during that time,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.50,0:09:23.10,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,絶園の樹の復活が\N間に合う希望はある≫
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.54,0:09:23.09,Defalics,,0,0,0,,there is still hope that the Tree of Exodus will be revived in time!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.51,0:09:27.12,Defalics,,0,0,0,,Even if the Tree of Genesis
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.60,0:09:27.14,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,≪たとえ\N本当に　はじまりの樹が→
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.12,0:09:29.78,Defalics,,0,0,0,,really {\i0}did{\i1} cause Mahiro's sister's death,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.14,0:09:29.91,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,真広の妹の死を\N招いたのだとしても→
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.78,0:09:32.17,Defalics,,0,0,0,,I must go back there!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.91,0:09:32.24,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,私は　そちらに戻らねばならん≫
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.17,0:09:34.31,Defalics,,0,0,0,,If I don't, I cannot do anything!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.24,0:09:34.51,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,≪戻らねば　何もできん≫
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.31,0:09:35.73,Defalics,,0,0,0,,I cannot make amends...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.51,0:09:36.51,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,≪何も償えん≫
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.42,0:09:43.47,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,≪いや　はじまりの樹といえど→
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.61,0:09:41.60,Defalics,,0,0,0,,No...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.60,0:09:43.52,Defalics,,0,0,0,,Even if it is the Tree of Genesis,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.47,0:09:47.37,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,それほど　精緻に\N理を　操れるものなのか？≫
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.52,0:09:46.89,Defalics,,0,0,0,,does it really wield that much power over logic?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.37,0:09:49.41,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,≪あくまで　偶然が重なって→
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.55,0:09:52.72,Defalics,,0,0,0,,Shouldn't I consider all of this just a series of coincidences?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.41,0:09:53.51,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,そんな状況が作られたと\N考えるべきではないのか？≫
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.51,0:09:58.07,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,≪はじまりの樹が　そこまで\N都合よく奇跡を呼べるのなら→
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.66,0:09:54.94,Defalics,,0,0,0,,If the Tree of Genesis
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.94,0:09:57.58,Defalics,,0,0,0,,could conjure miracles in my favor so easily,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.07,0:10:01.27,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,とうに　供物は\N見つかっているはずではないか≫
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.15,0:10:01.02,Defalics,,0,0,0,,shouldn't I have found the offering by now?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.04,0:10:06.64,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,≪これほどまでに　私が求め→
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.11,0:10:09.05,Defalics,,0,0,0,,It wishes me to find it, and yet...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.64,0:10:10.08,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,見つかるのを\N望んでいるというのに…≫
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.08,0:10:12.43,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,≪そうだ…　やはり→
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.47,0:10:11.74,Defalics,,0,0,0,,Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.74,0:10:16.06,Defalics,,0,0,0,,It couldn't have arranged the circumstances of Mahiro's sister's death.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.43,0:10:16.03,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,はじまりの樹が　真広の妹の死を\N作り出したわけでは…≫
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.87,0:10:27.40,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,≪ゴオオォーーー…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.40,0:10:29.80,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,≪ドーーン！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.17,0:10:36.69,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,≪そんな…≫
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.19,0:10:35.14,Defalics,,0,0,0,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.69,0:10:38.74,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,≪まさか…≫
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.95,0:10:37.95,Defalics,,0,0,0,,Impossible.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.70,0:10:40.08,Defalics,,0,0,0,,This can't be—
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.74,0:10:40.74,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,≪そんなことが…≫
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.56,0:10:59.38,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（葉風）ミサイル？→
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.87,0:10:58.21,Defalics,,0,0,0,,A missile?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.33,0:11:01.71,Defalics,,0,0,0,,How did such a product of civilization
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.38,0:11:04.20,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,こんな文明の産物が\Nなぜ　都合よく私のもとに…。
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.71,0:11:04.22,Defalics,,0,0,0,,appear before me so easily?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.06,0:11:18.00,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,≪左門の隠した供物は\N容易に見つからない≫
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.14,0:11:17.45,Defalics,,0,0,0,,I was having trouble finding the offering Samon hid,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.00,0:11:22.60,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,≪ならばと　私に\Nまったく別の供物を送り届けたか≫
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.07,0:11:22.62,Defalics,,0,0,0,,so it sent me another instead.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.84,0:11:29.22,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,≪はじまりの樹が\Nここまで　理を操れるのなら→
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.91,0:11:28.46,Defalics,,0,0,0,,If the Tree of Genesis can manipulate the natural order to this degree,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.18,0:11:33.07,Defalics,,0,0,0,,it's reasonable to assume it could have killed
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.22,0:11:33.18,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,高校生の妹一人を\N都合のよいときに殺すなど→
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.07,0:11:35.28,Defalics,,0,0,0,,a simple high school student's sister.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.18,0:11:35.48,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,造作もないではないか…≫
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.88,0:11:39.22,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（通信）葉風さん？→
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.01,0:11:37.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Ms. Hakaze,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.22,0:11:41.22,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,どうかしましたか？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.25,0:11:40.66,Default,,0,0,0,,is something wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.60,0:11:47.06,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（葉風）いや　供物が手に入った。\N（通信）えっ？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.66,0:11:43.41,Default,,0,0,0,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.15,0:11:45.86,Default,,0,0,0,,I found the offering.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.86,0:11:46.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.06,0:11:49.06,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,そちらに戻るぞ。
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.34,0:11:49.07,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm coming back.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.60,0:11:58.62,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,吉野　そちらの人形を\N私の骨に掛けろ。→
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.82,0:11:58.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Yoshino, put the doll close to my skeleton.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.62,0:12:02.18,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,骨と人形　２つで位置を確定する。
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.74,0:12:00.04,Default,,0,0,0,,I will determine the location
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.04,0:12:02.21,Default,,0,0,0,,using the skeleton and the doll.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.18,0:12:04.23,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,はい　分かりました。
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.53,0:12:03.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Understood.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.05,0:12:10.08,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（葉風）≪ふざけるな≫
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.42,0:12:09.76,Defalics,,0,0,0,,Don't be foolish.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.08,0:12:12.12,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,≪ここで折れてなるものか≫
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.42,0:12:12.63,Defalics,,0,0,0,,I cannot waver here!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.12,0:12:14.15,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（通信）準備できました。
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.63,0:12:13.80,Default,,0,0,0,,It's ready.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.80,0:12:17.80,Defalics,,0,0,0,,Even if the Tree of Genesis doesn't desire it,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.15,0:12:18.06,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,≪たとえ　それが　はじまりの樹が\N望まぬことであっても→
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.80,0:12:20.34,Defalics,,0,0,0,,I will find the one who killed Mahiro's sister,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.06,0:12:22.13,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,真広の妹を殺した犯人は\N必ず見つけてやる≫
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.34,0:12:21.74,Defalics,,0,0,0,,no matter what.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.13,0:12:26.22,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,≪私は　私のために戦った者を\N決して裏切らん≫
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.31,0:12:26.31,Defalics,,0,0,0,,I will never betray one who fought for my sake.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.25,0:12:31.64,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,樹の中の樹　大樹の中の大樹！→
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.36,0:12:29.79,Defalics,,0,0,0,,Tree within the tree,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.79,0:12:31.28,Defalics,,0,0,0,,great tree within the great tree,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.64,0:12:34.19,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,始まりにありし　はじまりの樹→
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.78,0:12:34.31,Defalics,,0,0,0,,tree that has existed since the beginning, Tree of Genesis.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.19,0:12:36.96,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,我が名は　鎖部葉風。
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.31,0:12:36.24,Defalics,,0,0,0,,My name is Kusaribe Hakaze.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.96,0:12:40.78,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,≪私は戻る　ここより先へ！≫
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.12,0:12:40.22,Defalics,,0,0,0,,I am returning, returning to the future.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.78,0:12:43.25,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（葉風）時の狭間を越えるため→
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.30,0:12:46.79,Defalics,,0,0,0,,To travel through time, by my proud name, hear my wish!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.25,0:12:46.65,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,かくも気高き名において\N聞き届けよ！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.34,0:13:12.38,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,なんだ!?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.85,0:13:11.82,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.38,0:13:14.75,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,こっ　これは…。
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.58,0:13:14.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Th-This is...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.45,0:13:32.50,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,≪時間の檻が…≫
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.71,0:13:32.42,Defalics,,0,0,0,,The prison of time...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.42,0:13:33.74,Defalics,,0,0,0,,It's been broken.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.50,0:13:34.59,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,≪破れた！≫
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.70,0:13:50.30,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（葉風）\Nああ…　こちらは冬だったか。
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.03,0:13:50.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, so it's winter here.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.44,0:13:55.82,Default,,0,0,0,,It seems I'll be cold in my present state.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.50,0:13:56.82,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（葉風）\Nさすがに　これでは寒いな。→
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.82,0:13:59.61,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,我が名は　鎖部葉風。
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.03,0:13:59.24,Default,,0,0,0,,I am Kusaribe Hakaze,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.61,0:14:01.80,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,はじまりの姫宮。
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.78,0:14:01.55,Default,,0,0,0,,the Princess of Genesis.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.52,0:14:09.55,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,２年の時を越え　帰って来たぞ。
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.58,0:14:09.79,Default,,0,0,0,,I've traveled two years through time to return.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.92,0:14:19.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Why are you naked, Ms. Hakaze?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.94,0:14:20.36,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,葉風さん　なんで裸なんですか!?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.36,0:14:23.96,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（葉風）着ているものまで\N再構成する余裕などあるか。
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.56,0:14:24.14,Default,,0,0,0,,I didn't have enough time to regenerate clothes on top of everything else.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.17,0:14:30.69,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（葉風）あれが真広か。→
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.28,0:14:30.15,Default,,0,0,0,,So that's Mahiro?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.69,0:14:34.73,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,なるほど　いかにもな顔つきだな。\Nだが→
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.72,0:14:33.67,Default,,0,0,0,,He's exactly as I imagined.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.67,0:14:36.04,Default,,0,0,0,,On the other hand, Yoshino...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.73,0:14:38.82,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,吉野　貴様は随分　幼い感じだな。
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.04,0:14:38.49,Default,,0,0,0,,You look surprisingly young.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.82,0:14:42.32,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ああも　抜け目なく立ち回れる\N悪党には見えんぞ？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.92,0:14:42.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Nothing like the villain your actions have made you out to be.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.95,0:14:48.79,Default,,0,0,0,,But I'm not a villain.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.04,0:14:49.54,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,いやいや　悪党じゃありませんって。\Nん？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.20,0:14:54.50,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,本物の銃ではないか。
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.42,0:14:54.52,Default,,0,0,0,,This looks like a real gun to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.50,0:14:57.45,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,貴様　やはり悪党であろう。
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.52,0:14:57.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Surely you must be a villain.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.41,0:14:59.57,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm telling you I'm not.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.45,0:14:59.45,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,だから違いますって。
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.75,0:15:04.22,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（葉風）左門　説明は不要であろう。
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.80,0:15:03.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Samon, I doubt an explanation is necessary.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.22,0:15:06.28,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,私に従え。→
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.43,0:15:05.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Obey me.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.28,0:15:09.28,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,だが\N貴様が間違っているかどうか→
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.40,0:15:09.36,Default,,0,0,0,,However, in my current state,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.28,0:15:11.55,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,今の私には分からん。→
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.36,0:15:11.59,Default,,0,0,0,,I cannot determine if you are right or wrong.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.55,0:15:14.89,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,これから\N何を選び　何をなすべきか→
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.59,0:15:15.00,Default,,0,0,0,,We must discuss what we should choose,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.89,0:15:17.39,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,互いに話し合わねばなるまい。→
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.00,0:15:17.15,Default,,0,0,0,,and what must be done from here on.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.15,0:15:20.23,Default,,0,0,0,,I am in no rush to dispose of the Tree of Exodus.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.39,0:15:20.29,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,絶園の樹の処置も　急ぐ気はない。
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.84,0:15:23.91,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（葉風）真広→
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.97,0:15:22.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Mahiro?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.91,0:15:27.28,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,かようなことになったが\N約束は守る。
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.99,0:15:26.91,Default,,0,0,0,,These are our circumstances, but I will keep my promise.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.28,0:15:30.20,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,はじまりの樹の企みが\N裏にあろうと→
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.49,0:15:30.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Even if the Tree of Genesis truly is behind this,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.20,0:15:33.85,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,必ず　貴様の前に\N犯人をひれ伏せさせる。
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.30,0:15:33.97,Default,,0,0,0,,I shall, without fail, bring the killer before you.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.85,0:15:35.85,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,今は　それで　こらえてくれ。
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.97,0:15:35.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Please accept this for now.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.50,0:15:40.48,Default,,0,0,0,,I am protected by the world's logic
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.76,0:15:42.78,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,私は　世の理の加護を受け\N時間さえ越えた者だぞ？→
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.48,0:15:42.30,Default,,0,0,0,,and have even traveled through time.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.78,0:15:44.80,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,この私が願うならば→
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.99,0:15:44.92,Default,,0,0,0,,If I were to wish it,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.80,0:15:49.12,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,たとえ　犯人が絶園の樹であろうと\N見つけられんわけがない。→
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.92,0:15:47.17,Default,,0,0,0,,even should the Tree of Exodus be the killer,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.17,0:15:49.22,Default,,0,0,0,,there's no reason I couldn't find the culprit.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.12,0:15:54.21,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,見つけられんなら　それは\Nはじまりの樹が犯人のときだけだ。
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.22,0:15:51.01,Default,,0,0,0,,The only scenario in which I couldn't
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.01,0:15:53.81,Default,,0,0,0,,would be if the Tree of Genesis were the killer.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.21,0:15:56.49,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,そのときは　私を殺せ。
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.44,0:15:56.62,Default,,0,0,0,,If that turns out to be the case, kill me.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.49,0:15:59.89,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,貴様の妹を殺したのは\N私も同然だ！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.62,0:15:59.53,Default,,0,0,0,,It would mean that I killed your sister!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.28,0:16:05.22,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ふっ　分かったよ。　なら　吉野→
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.08,0:16:03.26,Default,,0,0,0,,All right.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.89,0:16:04.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, Yoshino,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.22,0:16:09.07,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,お前も\N愛花の彼氏を教えるって約束…。
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.31,0:16:08.52,Default,,0,0,0,,you should keep your promise about Aika's boyf—
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.73,0:16:17.65,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（哲馬・通信）左門殿！\N哲馬か！　一体　何があった!?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.82,0:16:14.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Mr. Samon!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.92,0:16:17.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Tetsuma? What's going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.65,0:16:21.64,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（哲馬）はじまりの樹の強襲です！\N結界が破られます！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.83,0:16:19.88,Default,,0,0,0,,The Tree of Genesis has initiated an assault!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.88,0:16:21.91,Default,,0,0,0,,The barrier will be broken!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.64,0:16:23.65,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（左門・通信）はじまりの樹!?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.91,0:16:23.34,Default,,0,0,0,,The Tree of Genesis?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.21,0:16:36.85,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（山本）結界が　あんなに簡単に!?\N（潤一郎）あの結界自体→
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.48,0:16:35.09,Default,,0,0,0,,It penetrated the barrier that easily?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.09,0:16:37.09,Default,,0,0,0,,The barrier itself
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.85,0:16:39.94,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,はじまりの樹の力を借りて\N作ったものですから。
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.09,0:16:39.73,Default,,0,0,0,,was made with the Tree of Genesis's aid.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.94,0:16:43.81,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（夏村）結界は\N絶園の樹の制御もしていました。
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.12,0:16:43.48,Default,,0,0,0,,The barrier was controlling the Tree of Exodus.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.81,0:16:46.79,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,それを\Nいきなり消失させるなど…。
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.98,0:16:46.28,Default,,0,0,0,,If that barrier were to be suddenly obliterated—
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.79,0:16:50.45,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,潤一郎殿　一体\Nこれから　どうなるのです!?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.99,0:16:50.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Mr. Junichiro, what will happen now?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.45,0:16:53.92,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,分からない。　ただ→
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.69,0:16:51.78,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.35,0:16:53.44,Default,,0,0,0,,I only know
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.92,0:16:55.95,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,これからは嵐だ。
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.06,0:16:55.79,Default,,0,0,0,,that a storm is coming.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.95,0:16:59.06,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,あっ！\N（左門）はじまりの樹の覚醒か!?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.82,0:16:58.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Is the Tree of Genesis reviving?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.06,0:17:02.83,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,葉風さんが!?\Nいや　私は何も命じていない！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.12,0:17:00.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Is this your doing, Ms. Hakaze?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.27,0:17:02.80,Default,,0,0,0,,No, I haven't willed any of this to happen.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.43,0:17:07.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Mr. Samon,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.48,0:17:09.42,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,左門殿！\N絶園の樹は　我々の制御を離れ→
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.00,0:17:09.50,Default,,0,0,0,,the Tree of Exodus is attempting to break out of our control
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.42,0:17:12.22,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,はじまりの樹に\N応戦しようとしています！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.50,0:17:11.93,Default,,0,0,0,,and attack the Tree of Genesis!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.76,0:17:17.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Mr. Samon, what are your orders?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.76,0:17:18.06,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,左門殿　ご指示を!!　左門殿!!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.02,0:17:17.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Mr. Samon!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.05,0:17:24.78,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,どうした!?　哲馬～!!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.32,0:17:24.03,Default,,0,0,0,,What's wrong? Tetsuma!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.01,0:18:17.02,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（山本）これは　現実感ないわ…。
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.29,0:18:17.17,Default,,0,0,0,,This can't be real...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.02,0:18:20.35,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（夏村）このままでは\N狂嵐した絶園の樹によって→
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.17,0:18:20.55,Default,,0,0,0,,At this rate, the Tree of Exodus will go berserk
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.35,0:18:22.39,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,富士山麓は壊滅…→
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.55,0:18:22.34,Default,,0,0,0,,and destroy the entire area around Mt. Fuji.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.34,0:18:25.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Actually, this storm of destruction may end up
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.39,0:18:26.88,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,いえ　列島すら分断させかねない\N破壊の嵐が…。
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.54,0:18:26.96,Default,,0,0,0,,tearing the entire country apart.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.88,0:18:28.95,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（潤一郎）かもしれないね。
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.96,0:18:28.47,Default,,0,0,0,,It may be.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.95,0:18:32.95,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,でも　はじまりの樹は\Nこれで終わったわけじゃない。
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.18,0:18:33.10,Default,,0,0,0,,But the Tree of Genesis isn't done yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.62,0:18:56.44,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（山本）絶園の樹を食ってる!?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.86,0:18:56.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Is it eating the Tree of Exodus?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.28,0:19:03.28,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,防御！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.80,0:19:02.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Defense!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.80,0:19:10.00,Default,,0,0,0,,But Mr. Junichiro,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.85,0:19:09.89,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,しかし　潤一郎殿→
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.89,0:19:12.86,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,姫様が\N完全に覚醒を行っていないゆえ→
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.00,0:19:13.01,Default,,0,0,0,,since the princess hasn't conducted the final steps for the revival,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.86,0:19:15.81,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,現状では　絶園の樹が優勢では？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.01,0:19:15.64,Default,,0,0,0,,shouldn't the Tree of Exodus have the upper hand?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.64,0:19:17.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Judging by this area, yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.81,0:19:18.85,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ここだけ見ればね。\Nけど　たぶん→
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.56,0:19:23.10,Default,,0,0,0,,But the Tree of Genesis has most likely begun its revival across the world.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.85,0:19:23.35,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,はじまりの樹は\N世界中で覚醒を始めていると思う。
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.35,0:19:26.44,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,パリでもか！\N急いで確認しろ　今すぐに！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.60,0:19:24.23,Default,,0,0,0,,In Thailand, too?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.23,0:19:26.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Get a confirmation! Immediately!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.44,0:19:30.39,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,≪ニューヨークに巨大な樹が出現！\N≫ダメだ　情報が足りない！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.48,0:19:28.67,Default,,0,0,0,,A giant tree has appeared in New York!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.67,0:19:30.66,Default,,0,0,0,,It's no good! There's not enough information!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.39,0:19:32.63,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,≪あの文明を食ってる樹は→
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.66,0:19:32.79,Defalics,,0,0,0,,So that civilization-devouring tree
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.63,0:19:35.96,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,国内だけの現象じゃないのか!?≫
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.79,0:19:35.25,Defalics,,0,0,0,,wasn't limited to this country alone?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.96,0:19:38.36,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,我が名において聞き届けよ。
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.30,0:19:38.32,Defalics,,0,0,0,,Hear my name, and grant my wish!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.93,0:19:44.65,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,左門　復活の儀式は\Nどこでやっている？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.09,0:19:41.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Samon!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.39,0:19:44.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Where are they conducting the revival ceremony?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.65,0:19:48.36,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,それは…。\N儀式の場に相当量の供物があろう。
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.77,0:19:45.90,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't—
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.90,0:19:48.59,Default,,0,0,0,,There must be quite a few offerings at the site!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.36,0:19:51.50,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,それを使って\N私が絶園の樹を抑える。→
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.59,0:19:51.47,Default,,0,0,0,,I will use them to suppress the Tree of Exodus.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.47,0:19:54.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Simultaneously, I will halt the Tree of Genesis's revival.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.50,0:19:54.55,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,同時に\Nはじまりの樹の覚醒を止める。
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.55,0:19:58.95,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,信じろ！　はじまりの樹を\Nこのまま　完全覚醒させはせん！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.59,0:19:55.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Believe me!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.94,0:19:58.77,Default,,0,0,0,,I will not attempt to fully revive the Tree of Genesis now!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.69,0:20:03.69,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,分かりました…。
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.92,0:20:03.09,Default,,0,0,0,,All right then.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.48,0:20:07.78,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（局員）地震か!?\N（局員）でかいぞ！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.64,0:20:06.69,Default,,0,0,0,,An earthquake?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.69,0:20:07.78,Default,,0,0,0,,It's huge!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.39,0:20:20.49,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（早河）世界の…　関節が外れた…。
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.42,0:20:19.82,Default,,0,0,0,,The world is going insane...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.49,0:20:23.09,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,真広　その魔具をよこせ。→
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.94,0:20:22.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Mahiro, give me that talisman.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.91,0:20:24.87,Default,,0,0,0,,I will use it as an offering
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.09,0:20:26.86,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,それを供物にし直し\Nここの防御壁を強化する。
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.87,0:20:26.79,Default,,0,0,0,,to strengthen the defense here.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.79,0:20:31.35,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll strengthen this barrier enough that it will hold,\Neven if the Tree of Exodus attacks.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.86,0:20:31.27,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,この結界は　絶園の樹に\N直撃されても保つようにしておく。
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.27,0:20:35.32,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,私が大樹を鎮めに行っている間\N貴様たちは　ここを動くな。
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.35,0:20:34.76,Default,,0,0,0,,While I calm the great tree, you two stay here.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.32,0:20:37.37,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,はぁ…　分かったよ。
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.06,0:20:37.55,Default,,0,0,0,,All right.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.37,0:20:39.47,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,さっさと鎮めてきやがれ！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.55,0:20:39.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Hurry and calm it down.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.89,0:20:43.15,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（葉風）吉野。\Nえっ？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.12,0:20:42.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Yoshino.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.93,0:20:45.40,Default,,0,0,0,,I will be sure to thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.15,0:20:45.73,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,貴様には　あとで　必ず礼を…。
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.45,0:21:09.79,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（葉風）吉野～!!\N吉野!!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.76,0:21:08.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Yoshino!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.88,0:21:09.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Yoshino!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.79,0:21:11.99,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,少年！　不用意に動くな！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.83,0:21:11.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Young man, do not move!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.76,0:21:16.76,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（葉風）真広!!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.92,0:21:15.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Mahiro!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.37,0:21:22.29,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（山本）あっ…　彼は　どこ？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.80,0:21:22.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Where'd he go?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.29,0:21:25.12,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,潤一郎殿は　そういう方です。
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.46,0:21:25.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Mr. Junichiro is like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.12,0:21:28.02,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,どうにも捉えどころのない…　ん？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.19,0:21:27.34,Default,,0,0,0,,He's rather hard to read.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.88,0:21:34.81,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（山本）ここは　やばそうね。\Nあなたは　どうするの？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.08,0:21:32.60,Default,,0,0,0,,It's getting too dangerous here.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.23,0:21:34.98,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you going to do?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.81,0:21:38.45,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（夏村）鎖部夏村。\N（山本）えっ？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.98,0:21:36.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Kusaribe Natsumura.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.45,0:21:40.85,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,私の名前です。
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.04,0:21:40.83,Default,,0,0,0,,That is my name.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.96,0:21:47.41,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（山本）もし生き残れたら　お互い→
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.14,0:21:46.43,Default,,0,0,0,,If we survive this,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.43,0:21:49.94,Default,,0,0,0,,it seems we'll have a lot to talk about.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.41,0:21:50.78,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,腹を割って話す必要がありそうね。
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.78,0:21:53.28,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（夏村）独断では答えかねます。
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.95,0:21:53.05,Default,,0,0,0,,I am not at personal liberty to make that decision.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.80,0:21:59.81,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（左門）≪なんということだ…≫
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.98,0:21:59.87,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}How horrible...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.81,0:22:02.61,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,≪姫様が戻られた途端\Nもはや　二人は→
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.87,0:22:01.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Once the princess returned,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.64,0:22:04.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}these two were disposed of as though \Nthey were deemed no longer necessary.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.61,0:22:05.38,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,用済みとばかりに\N排除された≫
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.38,0:22:07.66,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,≪偶然か？　いや→
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.52,0:22:06.61,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Is it a coincidence?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.06,0:22:07.91,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Or...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.66,0:22:09.68,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,それとも　これが→
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.91,0:22:11.33,Default,,0,0,20,,{\i1}Could this be the logic of the Tree of Genesis?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.68,0:22:12.17,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,はじまりの樹の理なのか？≫
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.17,0:22:15.77,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（葉風）\N樹の中の樹　大樹の中の大樹！
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.29,0:22:13.82,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Tree within the tree,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.82,0:22:15.86,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}great tree within the great tree.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.77,0:22:19.08,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,まだ我の言葉を\N聞き届ける意思があるのなら→
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.86,0:22:18.86,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}If you still intend to heed my words,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.08,0:22:21.80,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,答えよ！
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.24,0:22:20.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}answer!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.80,0:22:25.45,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,姫様　そっ　それを使っては…。\N（葉風）左門！
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.99,0:22:23.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Princess, if you use that—
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.99,0:22:24.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Samon!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.45,0:22:28.45,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,お前は　真広を助けろ！\N私は　これから→
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.71,0:22:27.39,Default,,0,0,0,,You save Mahiro!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.39,0:22:31.67,Default,,0,0,0,,I will heal Yoshino as I head to the ritual site.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.45,0:22:31.86,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,吉野の体を修復しながら\N儀式場へ向かう！→
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.67,0:22:34.15,Default,,0,0,0,,You {\i1}must{\i0} save him, do you understand?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.86,0:22:33.96,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,いいか　絶対に助けろ！→
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.96,0:22:35.99,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,真広に何かあったら\N許さん！→
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.15,0:22:36.21,Default,,0,0,0,,I won't forgive you if anything happens to him!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.99,0:22:38.48,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,許さんからな!!\Nはい！→
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.21,0:22:37.30,Default,,0,0,0,,I will never forgive you!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.30,0:22:37.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Understood.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.88,0:22:47.99,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（葉風）≪吉野　死なせはせん≫
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.09,0:22:47.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Yoshino, I will not let you die.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.99,0:22:49.99,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,≪決して死なせんぞ≫
Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.19,0:22:49.58,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I will not!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.33,0:22:54.34,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,≪分からん≫
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.68,0:22:53.82,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I don't know...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:54.34,0:22:56.80,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,≪はじまりの樹は→
Dialogue: 0,0:22:54.53,0:22:56.11,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}What does
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.80,0:23:00.82,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,一体　私に　何を\N望んでいるのだ≫
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.94,0:23:00.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}the Tree of Genesis wish of me?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.00,0:23:18.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Oh, that cry did knock against my very heart!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.52,0:23:18.79,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,あの叫びが\N胸を打つ！→
Dialogue: 0,0:23:18.79,0:23:20.79,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,かわいそうに」。
Dialogue: 0,0:23:18.80,0:23:20.38,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Poor souls,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.62,0:23:24.92,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,「みんな\N溺れてしまった！」。
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.63,0:23:24.87,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}they perished.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.39,0:23:30.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Had I been any god of power,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.61,0:23:30.30,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,「私がもし力のある\N神様だったなら→
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.00,0:23:33.27,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I would have sunk the sea within the earth
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.30,0:23:33.10,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,海なんか\N陸の下に沈めてしまったのに」。
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.48,0:23:37.82,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,「そして　あの立派な船も→
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.56,0:23:40.43,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}or ere it should the good ship so have swallowed
Dialogue: 0,0:23:37.82,0:23:40.31,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,乗っていた人たちも→
Dialogue: 0,0:23:40.31,0:23:42.93,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,海に呑み込ませはしなかった」。
Dialogue: 0,0:23:40.43,0:23:42.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}and the fraughting souls within her.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:02.17,0:24:05.81,Default,,0,0,0,,While Aika was alive, I never got to ...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:05.81,0:24:08.82,Default,,0,0,0,,The softness of her skin, her warmth.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:09.69,0:24:11.38,Default,,0,0,0,,I never got to know them.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:11.80,0:24:13.09,Default,,0,0,0,,They all died.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:13.77,0:24:16.18,Default,,0,0,0,,The Tree of Genesis swallowed them all up.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:16.49,0:24:17.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Fuwa Mahiro,
Dialogue: 0,0:24:17.73,0:24:21.09,Default,,0,0,0,,could you kill Takigawa Yoshino?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:20.22,0:24:24.04,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（子供の吉野）\N死んだよ。　みんな死んじゃった。→
Dialogue: 0,0:24:21.09,0:24:24.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, that's probably about me.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:24.04,0:24:27.04,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,はじまりの樹が\N全部　飲み込んじゃったんだ。
